org.lfenergy.operatorfabric.users.model

Class UserSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lfenergy.operatorfabric.users.model.UserSettings

  • public class UserSettings
extends java.lang.Object
    User associated settings. Note that the current supported locales are en and fr. Date and time formats use Moment.js formats.
